            </div>
          </div>

          <h2>Key Factors</h2>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><strong>Parallel processing:</strong> Three tracks running simultaneously reduced total time</li>
            <li><strong>MOFA relationship:</strong> Same-day attestation through established coordination</li>
            <li><strong>Physical logistics:</strong> Document pickup, processing, and delivery managed as one service</li>
            <li><strong>Package organization:</strong> Documents arranged in GDRFA's preferred order with index sheet</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

